title: Gospel Fingers DVD - Piano Lessons
description:
Gospel Fingers gives you a mix of R&B, Jazz, Classical, and Contemporary gospel flavor.  From the beginner to the more advanced musician, this DVD takes you on a journey of phat flavorful chords for talk music, worship, traditional, stride piano, and much more.

GET IT IN ALL 12 gives you the tools needed to play effectively in all 12 keys.  This DVD gives you a step-by-step break down of what to play on each scale degree and how to quickly find that chord in every key.  It also shows you the most common progressions used in Gospel and R&B and how to play them in all keys.  Stop Trans "poising" and GET IT IN ALL 12.
